><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">String</span> country = <span class=\"built_in\">locale</span>.getCountry();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">String</span> lc=language+<span class=\"string\">\"_\"</span>+country;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> lc;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":11,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":11,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}]}